<paragraph xmlns:gate="http://www.gate.ac.uk" gate:gateId="0" gate:annotMaxId="240">Abravanel, <Location gate:gateId="183" rule1="Location1" locType="country" rule2="LocFinal">Maurice</Location>, conductor; <Event_Birth gate:gateId="239" RE="Jan. 6, 1903" Pred="birth" Pred-tyoe="time"><Birth gate:gateId="237" predict="birth">b.</Birth> Saloniki (<Location gate:gateId="184" rule1="Location1" locType="country" rule2="LocFinal">Greece</Location>), <Date gate:gateId="185" rule1="DateNameRev" kind="date" rule2="DateOnlyFinal">Jan. 6, 1903</Date></Event_Birth>. He studied at Lausanne Univ., and later in <Location gate:gateId="186" rule1="InLoc1" locType="city" rule2="LocFinal">Berlin</Location>. Leaving <Location gate:gateId="187" rule1="Location1" locType="country" rule2="LocFinal">Germany</Location> in <Date gate:gateId="188" rule1="YearContext1" kind="date" rule2="DateOnlyFinal">1933</Date> he conducted ballet in <Location gate:gateId="189" rule1="InLoc1" locType="city" rule2="LocFinal">Paris</Location> and <Location gate:gateId="190" rule1="Location1" locType="city" rule2="LocFinal">London</Location>; toured <Location gate:gateId="191" rule1="Location1" locType="country" rule2="LocFinal">Australia</Location> with the British National Opera Co. (193435). Conducted at Metropolitan Opera (<Date gate:gateId="193" rule1="TempYear3" kind="date" rule2="YearOnlyFinal">1936</Date>(<Date gate:gateId="194" rule1="TempYear3" kind="date" rule2="YearOnlyFinal">1940</Date>of the Utah State Symph. Orch. at <Location gate:gateId="196" rule1="Location1" locType="city" rule2="LocFinal">Salt Lake City</Location>. </paragraph>